"这里展示什么\n• 只收录当前会话中助手消息返回的图片。\n• 这些图片来自聊天回复，不是单独的图片生成工作台。\n\n可以做什么\n• 点按图片查看大图与对应提示词上下文。\n• 通过更多菜单保存到系统相册。\n• 删除图片会移除当前消息里的本地图片引用。\n\n使用建议\n• 继续生成或修改图片时，回到聊天里直接描述需求。\n• 需要整理历史结果时，先切到对应会话再打开相册。" = "What appears here\n• Only images returned by assistant messages in the current session are shown.\n• These images come from chat replies, not a separate image generation workspace.\n\nWhat you can do\n• Tap an image to view it with the related prompt context.\n• Use the more menu to save it to Photos.\n• Deleting an image removes the local image reference from the current message.\n\nTips\n• To continue or revise an image, go back to chat and describe what you need.\n• To organize older results, switch to that session before opening the album.";
