"主动检索长期记忆，用于在回答前补充用户历史偏好、长期背景和已记录事实。\n\n用法：\n1. mode=vector：语义相似检索，适合自然语言问题。\n2. mode=keyword：关键词命中检索，适合名称、术语、短语定位。\n3. count：希望返回的条数；未传时使用系统默认检索数量（Top K）。\n\n返回结果包含完整原文 content。若结果为空，表示当前记忆库无匹配项。" = "Actively search long-term memory to supplement the answer with the user's historical preferences, long-term background, and recorded facts before responding.\n\nUsage:\n1. mode=vector: semantic similarity search, suitable for natural-language questions.\n2. mode=keyword: keyword matching, suitable for names, terms, or phrases.\n3. count: desired number of results; when omitted, the system default Top K is used.\n\nResults include the full original content field. Empty results mean no matching memory was found.";
"Widget 标题（可选）。" = "Widget title (optional).";
"iOS 聊天内联 Widget 的 HTML 片段，可包含 style/script。片段会被插入 App 提供的固定画幅宿主容器；不要包含 html、head、body 或 viewport meta，也不要修改宿主页面。顶层内容应使用 100% 宽高填满容器，并根据容器尺寸响应式布局。" = "HTML fragment for an inline iOS chat widget; it may include style/script. The fragment is inserted into an app-provided host container with a fixed aspect ratio. Do not include html, head, body, or viewport meta, and do not modify the host page. Top-level content must fill 100% of the container's width and height and respond to its dimensions.";
"iOS 内联卡片的首选画幅，格式为“宽:高”，范围为 1:2 到 2:1，例如 16:9、4:3、1:1、3:4 或 9:16。宿主会填满气泡可用宽度，并根据此画幅计算固定高度。" = "Preferred aspect ratio for the iOS inline card, formatted as “width:height” and limited from 1:2 to 2:1, for example 16:9, 4:3, 1:1, 3:4, or 9:16. The host fills the bubble's available width and calculates a fixed height from this ratio.";
