"在 iOS 聊天中把传入的 HTML Widget 渲染为固定画幅的内联网页卡片。App 会将 widget_code 作为 HTML 片段插入宿主管理的容器，并根据气泡可用宽度与 inline_aspect_ratio 计算卡片高度；不要包含 html、head、body 或 viewport meta，也不要修改宿主页面。请让顶层内容使用 100% 宽高填满容器，并根据容器尺寸响应式布局。inline_aspect_ratio 和 widget_code 必填，title 和 loading_messages 可选。" = "On iOS, render the provided HTML widget as an inline web card with a fixed aspect ratio. The app inserts widget_code as an HTML fragment into a host-managed container and calculates the card height from the bubble's available width and inline_aspect_ratio. Do not include html, head, body, or viewport meta, and do not modify the host page. Make top-level content fill 100% of the container's width and height and respond to its dimensions. inline_aspect_ratio and widget_code are required; title and loading_messages are optional.";
"向用户展示结构化问答面板。支持 single_select / multi_select、可选的“其他输入”、必填校验与自定义提交按钮文案。此工具用于在回答前收集关键信息，调用后应等待用户补充。" = "Show a structured Q&A panel to the user. Supports single_select / multi_select, optional Other input, required validation, and custom submit button text. Use this to collect key information before answering; wait for the user's input after calling it.";
"把文本放入用户当前聊天输入框。text 为要填入的内容；mode=replace 会覆盖输入框，mode=append 会追加到末尾。适合为用户准备可编辑的草稿，而不是直接代替用户发送。" = "Place text into the user's current chat input box. text is the content to insert; mode=replace overwrites the box, mode=append appends to the end. Useful for preparing an editable draft for the user, not for sending on their behalf.";
"向反馈助手提交一条问题或建议工单。title 和 detail 必填；category 可选 bug 或 suggestion（默认 bug）；可附带复现步骤、预期行为、实际行为、补充信息。" = "Submit a bug or suggestion ticket to the feedback assistant. title and detail are required; category can be bug or suggestion (default bug); reproduction steps, expected behavior, actual behavior, and extra context may be included.";
"按路径名或 UTF-8 文本内容搜索应用沙盒 Documents 目录下的文件。只能访问沙盒内部路径。" = "Search files under the app sandbox Documents directory by path name or UTF-8 text content. Only sandbox-internal paths are accessible.";
"按行号分块读取应用沙盒 Documents 目录中的 UTF-8 文本文件，适合大文件场景。只能访问沙盒内部路径。" = "Read UTF-8 text files in the app sandbox Documents directory in line-based chunks, suitable for large files. Only sandbox-internal paths are accessible.";
"在应用沙盒 Documents 目录内移动或重命名文件、子目录。只能访问沙盒内部路径。" = "Move or rename files and subdirectories inside the app sandbox Documents directory. Only sandbox-internal paths are accessible.";
"在应用沙盒 Documents 目录内复制文件或子目录，可选是否覆盖已有路径。只能访问沙盒内部路径。" = "Copy files or subdirectories inside the app sandbox Documents directory, optionally overwriting existing paths. Only sandbox-internal paths are accessible.";
"在应用沙盒 Documents 目录内创建目录，可选自动创建父目录。只能访问沙盒内部路径。" = "Create directories inside the app sandbox Documents directory, optionally creating parent directories automatically. Only sandbox-internal paths are accessible.";
"按多条规则批量编辑应用沙盒 Documents 目录中的 UTF-8 文本文件。只能访问沙盒内部路径。" = "Batch edit UTF-8 text files in the app sandbox Documents directory using multiple rules. Only sandbox-internal paths are accessible.";
"分页列出长期记忆并支持关键词筛选，可选择是否包含归档记忆。" = "List long-term memories with pagination and keyword filtering, optionally including archived memories.";
"列出指定 SQLite 数据库（chat/config/memory）的表与字段结构，可选返回建表 SQL。" = "List tables and column schemas for the specified SQLite database (chat/config/memory), optionally returning CREATE TABLE SQL.";
"执行只读 SQL 查询。database 选择 chat/config/memory；sql 仅支持 SELECT/WITH/PRAGMA 且必须是单条语句；parameters 可选，用于按顺序绑定 ? 占位符；max_rows 默认 50。" = "Run a read-only SQL query. database is chat/config/memory; sql supports only SELECT/WITH/PRAGMA and must be a single statement; parameters optionally bind ? placeholders in order; max_rows defaults to 50.";
"执行写入 SQL。database 选择 chat/config/memory；sql 仅支持 INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE/REPLACE 且必须是单条语句；parameters 可选；UPDATE/DELETE 默认要求带 WHERE，除非 allow_without_where=true。" = "Run write SQL. database is chat/config/memory; sql supports only INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE/REPLACE and must be a single statement; parameters are optional; UPDATE/DELETE requires WHERE by default unless allow_without_where=true.";
