"这个页面适合做什么\n• 集中管理非核心聊天流程的进阶能力。\n• 快速进入维护、导入、调试等工具入口。\n\n各入口怎么选\n• 反馈助手：提交问题和追踪处理进度。\n• 远程文件访问：在局域网内访问 Documents 做排查或批量处理。\n• 存储管理：清理模型、文件、缓存，回收空间。\n• 导入数据：导入 ETOS 导出包或第三方应用迁移数据。\n\n使用建议\n• 不常用的功能可按需开启，避免主流程过载。\n• 涉及导入与清理时，建议先备份关键数据再执行。" = "What this page is for\n• Manage advanced capabilities outside the core chat flow.\n• Jump quickly into maintenance, import, and diagnostics tools.\n\nHow to choose an entry\n• Feedback: submit issues and track progress.\n• Remote File Access: inspect or batch-process Documents over your LAN.\n• Storage Management: clean up models, files, and caches.\n• Import Data: import ETOS export packages or migrate data from third-party apps.\n\nSuggestions\n• Enable infrequent features only when needed to keep the main flow focused.\n• Back up important data before import or cleanup operations.";
"通过局域网远程访问和管理 Documents 目录，方便命令行工具操作。" = "Access and manage the Documents directory over LAN for command-line workflows.";
"管理本地模型、文件与缓存占用。" = "Manage local model, file, and cache storage.";
"支持导入 ETOS 数据包，也可从 Cherry Studio 等来源迁移。" = "Import ETOS data packages, or migrate from sources such as Cherry Studio.";
"让 AI 在多轮对话里持续记住你的偏好、背景与目标。" = "Let AI keep track of your preferences, background, and goals across conversations.";
"能力说明\n• 记忆系统会在每次回复前参与检索，帮助模型关联你过去的偏好与上下文。\n• 与“世界书”不同，记忆系统是可持续积累、可读可写的动态知识。\n\n关键开关\n• 启用记忆功能：总开关。关闭后不会检索、也不会写入新记忆。\n• 允许写入新的记忆：仅控制“写入”，关闭后仍可读取已有记忆。\n\n推荐用法\n1. 先开启总开关观察回答是否更贴合长期习惯。\n2. 如果担心噪声记忆，先关闭写入，仅保留读取。\n3. 通过“记忆库管理”定期清理低质量或过时记忆。\n\n常见问题\n• 回答变得重复：可能记忆冗余，建议进入记忆库整理。\n• 明明开了但没效果：先确认会话未被世界书隔离策略屏蔽相关工具。" = "How it works\n• The memory system retrieves relevant history before each reply, helping the model connect your past preferences and context.\n• Unlike Worldbook, memory is dynamic knowledge that can accumulate, be read, and be written over time.\n\nKey switches\n• Enable memory: the main switch. When off, memory is neither searched nor written.\n• Allow writing new memories: controls writing only; existing memories can still be read when it is off.\n\nRecommended use\n1. Turn on the main switch first and see whether replies fit your long-term habits better.\n2. If noisy memories are a concern, disable writing and keep reading only.\n3. Clean up low-quality or stale memories periodically in Memory Library.\n\nCommon issues\n• Replies become repetitive: memory may be redundant; review the memory library.\n• Enabled but no effect: make sure this session is not blocking related tools through Worldbook isolation.";
"启用后，AI 会在响应前自动检索相关记忆，并可选择写入新的记忆片段。" = "When enabled, AI automatically retrieves relevant memories before responding and may write new memory snippets.";
"关闭后仅读取记忆，不会请求保存新内容。" = "When off, existing memories can still be read, but new content will not be saved.";
"会话摘要会写入会话 JSON；用户画像会保存到 Memory 目录下，并限制为每天最多更新一次。" = "Conversation summaries are written into session JSON; the user profile is saved under Memory and updated at most once per day.";
"集中管理内置记忆、拓展工具、MCP、Agent Skills 与快捷指令的聊天暴露状态。" = "Centrally manage chat exposure for built-in memory, app tools, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts.";
"适用场景\n• 你想快速判断“当前会话到底能用哪些工具”。\n• 你想统一调整不同类型工具的启用与审批策略。\n\n页面怎么看\n• 配置已启用：表示你在设置层面已打开。\n• 当前会话可用：在“总开关 + 审批策略 + 会话隔离”等条件下，聊天时真的可用。\n• 两个数字不一致通常不是 bug，而是被会话条件限制（例如世界书隔离发送）。\n\n推荐使用流程\n1. 先看概览区，确认五类工具的可用数量。\n2. 用“仅显示已启用”快速聚焦当前生效配置。\n3. 分别进入内置/拓展/MCP/Skills/快捷指令分类做单项微调。\n\n关键开关说明\n• 启用记忆系统：决定记忆相关内置工具是否可参与聊天。\n• 各分类“向模型暴露…工具”：控制该类工具是否整体开放给模型。\n• 审批策略：决定调用前是否确认、自动通过或拒绝。\n\n排查建议\n• 工具不生效：优先核对“当前会话可用”而不是“配置已启用”。\n• 会话隔离提示为橙色时：记忆、MCP、Agent Skills、快捷指令会被会话级策略屏蔽。" = "Use cases\n• Quickly check which tools are actually available in the current session.\n• Adjust enablement and approval policies for different tool categories in one place.\n\nHow to read this page\n• Configured enabled: enabled at the settings level.\n• Available in current session: truly available during chat after the main switch, approval policy, and session isolation are considered.\n• If the numbers differ, it is usually due to session conditions such as Worldbook isolation.\n\nRecommended flow\n1. Check the overview first to see available counts across the five tool groups.\n2. Use Enabled Only to focus on active configuration.\n3. Enter Built-in, App Tools, MCP, Skills, and Shortcuts categories for per-tool tuning.\n\nKey switches\n• Enable memory system: controls whether memory-related built-in tools can participate in chat.\n• Expose ... tools to model: controls whether each category is available to the model as a whole.\n• Approval policy: decides whether calls require confirmation, auto-allow, or denial.\n\nTroubleshooting\n• Tool not working: check Available in current session before Configured enabled.\n• When session isolation is orange, memory, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts may be blocked by session policy.";
"当前会话已启用世界书隔离发送，聊天时不会发送记忆、MCP、Agent Skills 与快捷指令工具。" = "Worldbook isolation is enabled for this session, so memory, MCP, Agent Skills, and Shortcuts tools will not be sent during chat.";
"统一查看已安装技能，并集中调整聊天暴露与单项启用状态。" = "Review installed skills and adjust chat exposure and per-skill enablement in one place.";
"总开关关闭后，下面的单项启用状态会保留，但聊天时不会实际暴露这些技能。" = "When the main switch is off, per-skill enablement is preserved but these skills are not exposed during chat.";
"当前还没有已安装技能，可在设置里的 Agent Skills 页面添加。" = "No skills are installed yet. Add them from the Agent Skills page in Settings.";
"当前还没有已安装技能，可在 Agent Skills 页面添加。" = "No skills are installed yet. Add them from the Agent Skills page.";
"当前会话因世界书隔离发送而不会实际启用该工具。" = "Memory and tools are disabled for the current chat, so this tool is not actually available.";
"该技能当前可参与聊天。" = "This skill can currently participate in chat.";

