"使用 action=read_resource 和对应 path 读取可读取的文本资源；大文件可额外提供 start_line 与 max_lines 分块读取；scripts/ 资源只会返回源码，不会执行。" = "Use action=read_resource with the matching path to read readable text resources. For large files, also provide start_line and max_lines to read by chunk. scripts/ resources return source only and are not executed.";
"使用 action=read_resource 和对应 path 读取可读资源；文本文件原样读取，docx/pptx/xlsx 与支持平台上的 PDF 会抽取纯文本；大文件可额外提供 start_line 与 max_lines 分块读取；scripts/ 资源只会返回源码，不会执行。" = "Use action=read_resource with the matching path to read readable resources. Text files are read as-is; docx/pptx/xlsx and PDF on supported platforms are extracted to plain text. For large files, also provide start_line and max_lines to read by chunk. scripts/ resources return source only and are not executed.";
