"高级区与导入" = "Advanced Area and Import";
"这里更接近 llama.cpp 底层能力，建议一次只改一类。" = "This area is closer to llama.cpp internals. Change only one category at a time.";
"KV Offload 和 Flash Attention 属于 Metal 稳定性开关；遇到 GPU/Metal 报错时先尝试关闭 Flash Attention 或 KV Offload。" = "KV Offload and Flash Attention are Metal stability switches. If GPU or Metal errors appear, try disabling Flash Attention or KV Offload first.";
"Grammar 适合约束 JSON、枚举或固定格式输出；语法不合法会直接影响生成。" = "Grammar is useful for constraining JSON, enums, or fixed-format output. Invalid grammar directly affects generation.";
"采样器链会改变候选 token 的处理顺序，建议只在你知道每个 sampler 作用时再自定义。" = "The sampler chain changes the order in which candidate tokens are processed. Customize it only when you know what each sampler does.";
"llama.cpp-style 参数导入只解析常用子集，导入后会变成表单覆盖项；App 不执行完整 CLI。" = "llama.cpp-style import only parses a common subset. Imported arguments become form overrides; the app does not run the full CLI.";
"常见排错路径" = "Common Troubleshooting";
"大多数问题可以先从文件、内存、输出上限和采样默认值排查。" = "Most issues can be checked first through the file, memory, output limit, and sampling defaults.";
"文件缺失时重新导入权重，或先停用该模型，避免聊天页继续选到它。" = "If the file is missing, reimport the weights or disable the model so chat does not keep selecting it.";
"加载慢通常来自大权重、大上下文或缓存未命中；可以降低上下文、减少 GPU 层数，或打开模型缓存。" = "Slow loading usually comes from large weights, a large context, or a cache miss. Lower the context, reduce GPU layers, or enable model cache.";
"输出短或提前结束时，检查最大输出 token、Grammar 和“忽略 EOS”。" = "If output is short or ends early, check Max Output Tokens, Grammar, and Ignore EOS.";
"回复发散、复读或格式不稳时，先恢复采样器链默认，再少量调整 Temperature、Top-P 和重复惩罚。" = "If replies drift, repeat, or lose formatting, restore the default sampler chain first, then lightly adjust Temperature, Top-P, and repetition penalties.";
"先读指南，再进入各参数二级页编辑；这样可以减少手表端误触。" = "Read the guide first, then edit parameters on their detail pages to reduce accidental taps on Apple Watch.";
"只覆盖必要项目" = "Override only what is needed";
"没有打开“自定义”的项目会继续使用 App 默认值或聊天页全局采样设置。" = "Items without Custom enabled keep using the app defaults or the global sampling settings from the chat page.";
"上下文越大越占内存；手表端建议从较小值开始，确认稳定后再提高。" = "Larger contexts use more memory. On Apple Watch, start smaller and raise it only after confirming stability.";
"这是单次回复的上限。手表端短问答可以压低，避免长时间高负载生成。" = "This is the limit for one reply. For short Q&A on Apple Watch, lower it to avoid long high-load generation.";
"不确定时先只调 Temperature；复读明显时再看重复检查窗口和重复惩罚。" = "If unsure, adjust only Temperature first. When repetition is obvious, check repeat window and repetition penalties.";
"参数怎么调" = "How to Tune";
"CPU 路径" = "CPU Path";
"模型大小" = "Model Size";
"手表端建议先用更小的 GGUF 和较短上下文，确认不会被系统回收后再提高参数。" = "On Apple Watch, start with a smaller GGUF and a shorter context. Raise parameters only after confirming the system does not reclaim the app.";
"手表端限制" = "Apple Watch Limits";
"文件与速度" = "File and Speed";
"文件缺失时重新下载或停用模型；生成很慢时先降低上下文长度和最大输出 token。" = "If the file is missing, download it again or disable the model. If generation is slow, lower context size and max output tokens first.";
