"进入后可重新生成全部嵌入，并查看每条记忆的处理状态。" = "Open this page to regenerate all embeddings and review each memory's processing status.";
"会清理旧的向量数据库，并按当前记忆重新生成嵌入。并发数量会自动保存。" = "This clears the old vector database and regenerates embeddings from the current memories. The concurrency setting is saved automatically.";
"添加记忆后可在这里重新生成嵌入。" = "After adding memories, you can regenerate embeddings here.";
"重新嵌入完成后会显示勾选标记；失败的记忆可点按单独重试。" = "Completed memories show a checkmark; tap failed memories to retry them individually.";
