"此操作会用 iCloud 的完整同步数据替换本机同步数据。请输入“%@”以确认覆盖；执行前会自动创建安全快照。" = "This replaces synchronized data on this device with the complete data from iCloud. Type “%@” to confirm. A safety snapshot is created first.";
"此操作会删除 iCloud 当前同步记录并上传本机完整数据，其他设备随后会以本机数据为准。请输入“%@”以确认覆盖；执行前会自动创建安全快照。" = "This deletes the current synchronized records in iCloud and uploads the complete data from this device. Other devices will then follow this device’s data. Type “%@” to confirm. A safety snapshot is created first.";
"使用此设备数据覆盖 iCloud" = "Replace iCloud with This Device";
"暂不同步" = "Not Now";
"此设备尚未建立可信的 iCloud 同步基线。本机有 %d 条记录，iCloud 有 %d 条记录；App 无法安全判断一端为空是首次接入还是有意删除。选择前不会修改任何数据，执行覆盖前会自动创建安全快照。" = "This device does not yet have a trusted iCloud sync baseline. It has %d local records and iCloud has %d. The app cannot safely tell whether an empty side means first setup or an intentional deletion. Nothing changes until you choose, and a safety snapshot is created before replacement.";
"等待选择数据来源" = "Waiting for Data Source";
"正在创建安全备份…" = "Creating a safety backup…";
"正在使用 iCloud 数据替换此设备…" = "Replacing this device with iCloud data…";
"正在使用此设备数据重建 iCloud…" = "Rebuilding iCloud from this device…";
"iCloud 新数据集校验失败，原有同步基线未被替换。" = "The new iCloud data set could not be verified. The existing sync baseline was not replaced.";
"iCloud 首次同步裁决说明" = "iCloud Roaming Sync uses per-record incremental changes, and every device keeps its own sync cursor. Enable it only when you need iPhone, iPad, or Apple Watch to share data through the same Apple ID. A single device, or a workflow that only needs manual snapshots, does not need it. After being offline, powered off, or unopened for a long time, a device fetches only changes it has not processed.\n\nCheck and Sync Now first downloads remote additions, edits, and deletions after the cursor. It recognizes and protects local pending changes and deletions so an older remote record cannot overwrite a deletion waiting to upload. It then uploads local additions, edits, and deletions, and saves the new cursor and baseline only after everything succeeds. It does not clear the cursor or force either side to replace the other.\n\nThe app pauses for a decision only when the device has no trusted baseline and its state differs from iCloud, even if either side is empty. After choosing either overwrite direction, you must type the confirmation phrase shown by the app. Using iCloud replaces synchronized local data completely. Using this device publishes a new cloud data generation that other devices then follow. A safety snapshot is created before either replacement.";
