// 内建个人数据 MCP 服务器
"内建个人数据" = "Built-in Personal Data";
"应用内建个人数据服务，无需配置网络地址；HealthKit 与 EventKit 权限仅在工具正式调用时申请。" = "App built-in personal data service. No network address is required; HealthKit and EventKit permissions are requested only when a tool is actually called.";
"提供 HealthKit 健康数据与 EventKit 日历/提醒事项工具。仅在工具正式调用时申请系统权限。" = "Provides HealthKit health data tools and EventKit calendar/reminder tools. System permissions are requested only when a tool is actually called.";
"工具正式调用时按单个 HealthKit 类型申请读取或写入权限。" = "When a tool is called, read or write permission is requested only for the selected HealthKit type.";
"列出当前内建 HealthKit 工具支持的健康数据类型、读写能力与默认单位。不会请求 HealthKit 权限。" = "Lists the health data types, read/write capabilities, and default units supported by the built-in HealthKit tools. Does not request HealthKit permission.";
"按 HealthKit 类型读取原始样本，例如 heart_rate、heart_rate_variability、sleep_analysis、workouts、body_mass。调用时仅请求所需类型的读取权限。" = "Reads raw samples by HealthKit type, such as heart_rate, heart_rate_variability, sleep_analysis, workouts, or body_mass. Requests read permission only for the required type.";
"按 HealthKit 数值类型读取统计结果，适合步数、活动能量、心率均值、HRV 均值等汇总查询。调用时仅请求所需类型的读取权限。" = "Reads statistics for HealthKit quantity types, useful for summaries such as step count, active energy, average heart rate, or average HRV. Requests read permission only for the required type.";
"写入允许记录的 HealthKit 数值样本，例如 dietary_water、dietary_caffeine、dietary_energy、body_mass。调用时仅请求该类型写入权限。" = "Writes allowed HealthKit quantity samples, such as dietary_water, dietary_caffeine, dietary_energy, or body_mass. Requests write permission only for that type.";
"写入允许记录的 HealthKit 分类样本，例如 mindful_session、headache、fever、coughing。调用时仅请求该类型写入权限。" = "Writes allowed HealthKit category samples, such as mindful_session, headache, fever, or coughing. Requests write permission only for that type.";
"查询指定时间段内的系统日历事件，包含标题、地点、起止时间、备注和参与人摘要。调用时请求日历完整访问权限。" = "Queries system calendar events in a time range, including title, location, start/end time, notes, and attendee summary. Requests full calendar access when called.";
