// 语音输入设置介绍
"启用语音输入" = "Enable voice input";
"模型支持时发送音频" = "Send audio when supported";
"语音输入模式" = "Voice input mode";
"录音后可先转写到输入框，也可在模型支持音频输入时作为音频附件发送。" = "Recordings can be transcribed into the input field, or sent as audio attachments when the model supports audio input.";
"语音转写\n• 关闭“模型支持时发送音频”时，录音会先发送给语音识别模型转写。\n• 识别结果会先进入预览，点完成后再补到输入框；取消会丢弃本次结果。\n\n音频直发\n• 开启“模型支持时发送音频”时，录音会作为音频附件发送给当前聊天模型。\n• 只有当前聊天模型在模型设置中开启“可处理音频”，并且提供商实际支持音频输入时，才适合使用音频直发。\n• 如果当前聊天模型不支持音频输入，请关闭该开关，改用语音识别模型转写。\n\n模型选择\n• 语音识别模型可以在本页选择，也可以在“提供商与模型管理 > 专用模型”中统一设置。" = "Speech transcription\n• When “Send audio when supported” is off, recordings are sent to the speech recognition model for transcription.\n• Results are previewed first and appended to the input field only after you tap Done; Cancel discards this result.\n\nDirect audio\n• When “Send audio when supported” is on, recordings are sent to the current chat model as audio attachments.\n• Use this only when the current chat model has “Can process audio” enabled in model settings and the provider actually supports audio input.\n• If the current chat model does not support audio input, turn this off and use speech transcription instead.\n\nModel selection\n• You can choose the speech recognition model here, or configure it globally in Providers & models > Specialized models.";
"录音可用系统内建识别或 OpenAI Audio Transcriptions 兼容模型转写，也可在聊天模型支持音频时直发。" = "Recordings can be transcribed with the built-in system recognizer or an OpenAI Audio Transcriptions compatible model, or sent directly when the chat model supports audio.";
"语音输入模式详情：转写接口与模型来源" = "Speech transcription\n• When “Send audio when supported” is off, recordings are sent to the speech recognition model for transcription.\n• Results are previewed first and appended to the input field only after you tap Done; Cancel discards this result.\n• The model list includes the built-in SFSpeechRecognizer, which can use system speech recognition directly.\n\nSpeech model format\n• Third-party speech recognition models must be compatible with the OpenAI Audio Transcriptions API: POST /audio/transcriptions, multipart/form-data with file and model, returning a text field.\n• Because the add-model flow is not a good place for another protocol switch, the app does not mark this format separately in model capabilities. Please confirm support from provider docs or your own tests.\n• Services such as FunAudioLLM/SenseVoiceSmall can be used as speech recognition models if they are compatible with this API.\n• Where can you find these models? This app does not advertise providers; you can ask AI to help find speech recognition APIs or local deployment options compatible with OpenAI Audio Transcriptions.\n\nDirect audio\n• When “Send audio when supported” is on, recordings are sent to the current chat model as audio attachments.\n• Use this only when the current chat model has “Can process audio” enabled in model settings and the provider actually supports audio input.\n• If the current chat model does not support audio input, turn this off and use speech transcription instead.\n\nModel selection\n• You can choose the speech recognition model here, or configure it globally in Providers & models > Specialized models.";
"语音转写\n• 关闭“模型支持时发送音频”时，录音会先发送给语音识别模型转写。\n• 识别结果会先进入预览，点完成后再补到输入框；取消会丢弃本次结果。\n• 模型列表里包含系统内建的 SFSpeechRecognizer，可直接使用系统语音识别。\n\n语音识别模型格式\n• 第三方语音识别模型需要兼容 OpenAI Audio Transcriptions 接口：POST /audio/transcriptions，multipart/form-data 上传 file 和 model，并返回 text 字段。\n• 因为添加模型的界面不适合再增加专门协议开关，App 不会在模型能力里单独标记这个格式；请按提供商文档或自测结果判断是否支持。\n• FunAudioLLM/SenseVoiceSmall 这类服务如果已经兼容该接口，就可以作为语音识别模型使用。\n\n音频直发\n• 开启“模型支持时发送音频”时，录音会作为音频附件发送给当前聊天模型。\n• 只有当前聊天模型在模型设置中开启“可处理音频”，并且提供商实际支持音频输入时，才适合使用音频直发。\n• 如果当前聊天模型不支持音频输入，请关闭该开关，改用语音识别模型转写。\n\n模型选择\n• 语音识别模型可以在本页选择，也可以在“提供商与模型管理 > 专用模型”中统一设置。" = "Speech transcription\n• When “Send audio when supported” is off, recordings are sent to the speech recognition model for transcription.\n• Results are previewed first and appended to the input field only after you tap Done; Cancel discards this result.\n• The model list includes the built-in SFSpeechRecognizer, which can use system speech recognition directly.\n\nSpeech model format\n• Third-party speech recognition models must be compatible with the OpenAI Audio Transcriptions API: POST /audio/transcriptions, multipart/form-data with file and model, returning a text field.\n• Because the add-model flow is not a good place for another protocol switch, the app does not mark this format separately in model capabilities. Please confirm support from provider docs or your own tests.\n• Services such as FunAudioLLM/SenseVoiceSmall can be used as speech recognition models if they are compatible with this API.\n\nDirect audio\n• When “Send audio when supported” is on, recordings are sent to the current chat model as audio attachments.\n• Use this only when the current chat model has “Can process audio” enabled in model settings and the provider actually supports audio input.\n• If the current chat model does not support audio input, turn this off and use speech transcription instead.\n\nModel selection\n• You can choose the speech recognition model here, or configure it globally in Providers & models > Specialized models.";

